data.description: Outstanding 1 acre plus horse property! The home itself boasts 5 spacious beds, & 3 full baths. Inside you'll discover an open floor plan living and dining area in a bright and light interior that comes w/vinyl plank flooring t/out, large windows, ceiling fans, & tons of natural light. The kitchen comes complete w/plenty of cabinets/counter space, & essential appliances. Main bedroom enjoys a walk-in closet and en suite w/dual sinks, garden tub, & separate shower. Enjoy relaxing in the long elevated ( wrap around) deck with breath taking mountain views that invite comfort and peace.Bring all your toys and animals and start to realize the farm ranch of your dreams. MOTIVATED SELLER, ALL OFFERS WELCOMED!
